channel.title: I'm the luckiest person in the world!
channel.description: yup, i just won tickets to the virgin festival in maryland.featuring: Red Hot Chili Peppers, The Who, The Killers, The Flaming Lips, The Raconteurs, Gnarls Barkley, Scissor Sisters, Thievery Corporation, Clap Your Hands Say Yeah, The New Pornographers, Drive-By Truckers, Kasabian, Brazilian Girls, Wolfmother. DJ Tent featuring: Tiesto, John Digweed, Carl Cox, RJD2, 2ManyDJs, James Holden. i won it off a local radio and i'm more excited about this than anything that's happened in the last couple years it's tomorrow (saturday) and i'm so pumped... just wanted to let you guys know :)
